line_1: An' hear it a', an' fear an' tremble!
line_2: While they maun stan' , wi' aspect humble,

line_1: And then to hear the Lye, would make one Tremble.
line_2: If we can Swear and Lye, you can Dissemble,

line_1: I smile, she cry'd, but ah! I tremble,
line_2: Which Damon then will most resemble.
